  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy of a nasopore sponge dressing soaked in Bacitracin VS a
      sponge soaked in Saline / and the administration of oral antibiotics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Same as above
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
